    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坂本龙马安排萨摩藩和长州藩结盟，以联合起来打败幕府。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，在萨长联盟期间，突然出现了一个虫洞，在场的人都被传送到了蓬莱仙境！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在蓬松乐园中找到散落在各处的伟大人物，让萨长联盟取得成功！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >低度子弹射击游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坂本龙马拥有时间停止和瞬间移动的能力（教科书上没有）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你无法躲避子弹！如果你认为无法躲避子弹，请停止时间并移动到安全的地方！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当光标在时间停止的状态下触碰到子弹时，坂本龙马的枪就会启动！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吸收子弹能量，发动强力攻击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏中出现的著名人物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坂本龙马</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日本江户时代末期的土佐藩武士，拥有随时停止时间和穿越的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在萨乔联盟中，他被传送到了蓬莱大陆，但他仍然没有放弃萨乔联盟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他根本不会说话。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095650/extras/9fd9341e0920345a8549ac17d34e3f62.avif?t=1750264815\" width=396 height=748 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >西乡隆盛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >萨摩藩的首领，能让时间停止。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他认为萨超联盟期间出现的虫洞都是长州一族造成的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095650/extras/e1f4a8d3c3f8667a8047503abf6d7d93.avif?t=1750264815\" width=600 height=531 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >涩泽荣一。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个最近在日本成为万日元纸币的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他站在幕府一边，但在调查萨超联盟时被卷入虫洞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095650/extras/03698b0c1082f90d9fc34d21400ee2e3.avif?t=1750264815\" width=600 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >马修-佩里</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乘坐黑船来到日本的美国人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与萨超联盟无关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他正在敦促蓬莱乐园向日本人开放。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095650/extras/23ffa83d3b03558e35053b103c485bac.avif?t=1750264815\" width=358 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >致视频撰稿人和发行人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请阅读[Retsu Teikoku]游戏现场报道指南。</p>",
